data.description: Beautiful home with curb appeal located in the city limits of Fallon.   1762 square feet with 4 bedrooms, 2 baths and an attached 3 car garage.   Kitchen is spacious with lots of cabinets, pantry and a breakfast nook.  Master suite has double sinks, shower stall and jetted bath tub.   The back yard is large, fully fenced, landscaped, has a covered back patio, 1 car detached garage/shop and a chicken coop.
